cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.LG 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to identify hazardous products from online reviews. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) to extract relevant information from reviews, and machine learning (cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.LG) to train a classifier to identify hazardous products.
